      "content": "honestly i feel like i'm just a ghost here. like i walk through these streets in a city where nobody knows my name and it doesn't even matter if i'm here or not. if i just... stopped existing tomorrow, i don't think a single person would even blink. it's like i'm just taking up space for no reason.",
